# Netflix Filming Locations in London You Can Actually Visit

<img 
  src="https://i.ibb.co/LbT4hs3/Chat-GPT-Image-May-30-2025-02-02-11-AM.png" 
  alt="Map showing Netflix filming locations around London"
  style="width: 100%; max-height: 500px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px;"
/>

## Introduction

Ever watched a Netflix show and wondered *where they actually filmed that scene*? London is no stranger to the spotlight, serving as the real-world backdrop for some of Netflix’s most beloved series and films.

In this post, we’re spotlighting 5 iconic Netflix productions that used London as their filming playground. We’ve included maps, descriptions, and tips for visiting these real-world locations — perfect for your next movie-inspired adventure in the capital.

## 5 Netflix Filming Locations in London You Can Visit

<div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; margin: 30px 0;">
  <img 
    src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS7DVJBus36QzyBFO5Wp_ko-pQADyv6kM3Aag&s" 
    alt="Lancaster House from The Crown"
