## Conclusion

London’s film history is deeper than the studios suggest — its streets, palaces, and parks are regularly transformed into storybook settings.

This guide offers a chance to literally walk in the footsteps of your favorite Netflix characters. From royal dramas to gritty street sagas, these real locations bring the screen to life in the most exciting way possible.

Which Netflix filming location in London surprised you the most? Let us know — or suggest one we should add next!

